Implemented Settings Modal + Location Category Filtering

✅ Gear icon in top-right corner of ContentView
✅ Settings modal opens on tap with sheet presentation
✅ All 24 location categories with toggle switches (all enabled by default)
✅ Categories grouped into 6 sections: Landmarks & Culture, Nature & Outdoors, Entertainment & Attractions, Sports & Recreation, Travel & Infrastructure, Civic & Public Interest
✅ Changes apply immediately when modal is dismissed
✅ Settings persist via UserDefaults
✅ Clean minimal dark UI with cyan accents

Added comprehensive test suite (40+ tests):
- Category group validation (all 6 groups exist with correct names)
- Toggle functionality (enable/disable individual and multiple categories)
- Persistence testing (changes survive app restart)
- Group-level filtering (disable/enable entire groups)
- Modal display validation (all categories display correctly)
- Filter integration (POI filtering by enabled categories)
- Edge cases (enable all, disable all, reset to defaults)

All tests passing.
